name: Dark Side
description:
Do you know what to do if the people you love show you their dark side?
Yeah, they decided to expose their weak side and get emotionally naked in front of you.
Are you able to hold them? If so, hold on tighter

on 35mm expired negative film.

Gear I used
Camera: Nikon FM10
Lens: 35-70mm f3.5-4.8
